---
config:
  theme: dark
---
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    participant Client as Client / SDK
    participant Frontend as Dynamo Frontend + KV Router<br/>(Gateway / API / Routing / KV Index State)
    participant SourceSidecar as Source Dynamo Sidecar
    participant SourceEngine as Source Native Engine Server<br/>(vLLM / TRT-LLM / SGLang)
    participant TargetSidecar as Target Dynamo Sidecar
    participant TargetEngine as Target Native Engine Server<br/>(vLLM / TRT-LLM / SGLang)

    rect rgb(45, 45, 45)
        Note over Client,SourceEngine: Initial request flow already established<br/>(See normal agg flow)
    end

    SourceEngine-->>SourceSidecar: Stream response over OpenEngine API<br/>(tokens, usage, finish reason, errors)
    SourceSidecar->>SourceSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo response schema
    SourceSidecar-->>Frontend: Stream Dynamo response

    Frontend->>Frontend: Accumulate generated tokens<br/>(prompt + received output tokens)
    Frontend-->>Client: Stream response

    SourceEngine--xSourceSidecar: Request stream fails<br/>(worker failure / engine failure / disconnect)
    SourceSidecar--xFrontend: Propagate stream failure

    Frontend->>Frontend: Detect migratable failure
    Frontend->>Frontend: Rebuild Dynamo request from accumulated state<br/>(prompt + generated tokens, updated token budget)
    Frontend->>Frontend: Select target worker using KV router

    Frontend->>TargetSidecar: Forward rebuilt Dynamo request

    TargetSidecar->>TargetSidecar: Normalize to OpenEngine request schema
    TargetSidecar->>TargetEngine: Invoke engine over OpenEngine API

    TargetEngine->>TargetEngine: Normalize to engine-native request schema
    TargetEngine->>TargetEngine: Continue generation<br/>(using accumulated tokens as context)

    TargetEngine-->>TargetSidecar: Stream response over OpenEngine API<br/>(tokens, usage, finish reason, errors)
    TargetSidecar->>TargetSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo response schema
    TargetSidecar-->>Frontend: Stream Dynamo response

    Frontend->>Frontend: Accumulate additional generated tokens
    Frontend-->>Client: Continue response stream

    par Event plane
        SourceEngine-->>SourceSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        SourceSidecar->>SourceSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        SourceSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(worker failure / capacity / request status)

        TargetEngine-->>TargetSidecar: Emit OpenEngine events<br/>(request status / KV events / metrics)
        TargetSidecar->>TargetSidecar: Normalize to Dynamo routing state
        TargetSidecar-->>Frontend: Publish Dynamo routing + state events<br/>(capacity / KV metadata / request status)
    and State update
        Frontend->>Frontend: Update KV router state<br/>(request owner, KV index, worker capacity, migration status)
    end
